---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="description" content="프레임워크 마이그레이션을 위한 전문 가이드 플랫폼" />
    <title>Migration eBooks - 프레임워크 마이그레이션 가이드</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --sl-color-accent: 255, 93, 1;
        --sl-color-accent-high: 255, 120, 51;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: white;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        width: 100%;
      }

      header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #f0f0f0);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        font-weight: 300;
      }

      .books-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }

      .book-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .book-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      .book-card.available {
        border-color: rgba(76, 217, 100, 0.5);
      }

      .book-card.coming-soon {
        opacity: 0.7;
        cursor: not-allowed;
      }

      .book-title {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .book-desc {
        font-size: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        flex-grow: 1;
      }

      .book-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .badge-available {
        background: rgba(76, 217, 100, 0.2);
        color: #4cd964;
      }

      .badge-coming-soon {
        background: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.2);
        color: #ffcc00;
      }

      .stats {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .stat-item {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border-radius: 0.75rem;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      }

      .stat-number {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .stat-label {
        opacity: 0.8;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 4rem;
        opacity: 0.7;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      footer a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
          font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .books-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>Migration eBooks</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          프레임워크 마이그레이션을 위한 완벽한 가이드
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="books-grid">
        <a href="/migrations/angular-to-react/" class="book-card available">
          <div>
            <h2 class="book-title">Angular → React</h2>
            <p class="book-desc">
              Angular 애플리케이션을 React로 마이그레이션하는 완벽한 가이드.
              150개 이상의 실제 코드 예제와 5개의 파트로 구성된 전문 eBook.
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="book-badge badge-available">✓ 이용 가능</span>
        </a>

        <div class="book-card coming-soon">
          <div>
            <h2 class="book-title">React → Vue</h2>
            <p class="book-desc">
              React 애플리케이션을 Vue 3 (Composition API)로 마이그레이션하는 가이드.
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="book-badge badge-coming-soon">⏰ 준비 중</span>
        </div>

        <div class="book-card coming-soon">
          <div>
            <h2 class="book-title">Vue → Svelte</h2>
            <p class="book-desc">
              Vue 애플리케이션을 Svelte/SvelteKit로 마이그레이션하는 가이드.
            </p>
          </div>
          <span class="book-badge badge-coming-soon">⏰ 준비 중</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">150+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">코드 샘플</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">70+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">페이지</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">5</span>
          <span class="stat-label">실전 케이스</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">무료</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <footer>
        <p>
          오픈소스 프로젝트 ·
          <a href="https://github.com/thatseeai/migrations" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
